    public static class DTUHypothesis.PendingPhrase<TK,FV>
extends Object
implements Comparable<DTUHypothesis.PendingPhrase<TK,FV>>
    This class represents a phrase with one or more discontinuities in its target side. It holds this information: abstract translation option is used to generate the discontinuous phrase, and index of the current contiguous segment.
